          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_2_p_7"><b>Annex B – Hansard References</b></p>
            <p>The following table sets out the dates and Hansard references for each stage of the Act’s passage through Parliament.</p>
            <table uk:widths="2.25in 1.34in 2.16in">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Stage</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Date</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Hansard reference</b></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p>House of Commons</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Introduction</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>15 June 2022</p>
